cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "claude-router: local embedding-based model-tier and scaffold routing for Claude"
abstract: >-
  claude-router is an AI reliability tool that classifies each prompt locally
  with an embedding model, then routes it to the right Claude tier and prepends
  a task-specific scaffold only when scaffolding measurably improves quality —
  closing the silent failure mode where teams default to Sonnet or Opus and
  overspend without a repeatable rule for when a cheaper tier plus structure is
  enough.
